      <title>Github Rookies</title>
      <link href="/posts/106702426/"/>
      <url>/posts/106702426/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="To-Create-a-New-Repository"><a href="#To-Create-a-New-Repository" class="headerlink" title="To Create a New Repository"></a>To Create a New Repository</h2><ol><li>Repository name</li><li>Description</li><li>Public / Private</li><li>Initialize this repository with a README</li><li>Add .gitignore</li><li>Add a license</li></ol><h2 id="To-Connect-the-Repository"><a href="#To-Connect-the-Repository" class="headerlink" title="To Connect the Repository"></a>To Connect the Repository</h2><p><a href="https://github.com:Alowree/Hello-World">https://github.com:Alowree/Hello-World</a></p><ol><li>README.md</li><li>Github Flavored Markdown</li></ol><h2 id="To-Publish-Code-on-Github"><a href="#To-Publish-Code-on-Github" class="headerlink" title="To Publish Code on Github"></a>To Publish Code on Github</h2><ol><li><code>git clone</code> repository to local</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> git@github.com:Alowree/Hello-World.git</span><br><span class="line">Cloning into <span class="string">&#x27;Hello-World&#x27;</span>...</span><br><span class="line">remote: Enumerating objects: 3, <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">remote: Counting objects: 100% (3/3), <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">remote: Total 3 (delta 0), reused 0 (delta 0), pack-reused 0</span><br><span class="line">Receiving objects: 100% (3/3), <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><p>Create a code file locally, write some codes, and save the file.</p></li><li><p>Check with <code>git status</code> command</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> Hello-World</span><br><span class="line">$ git status</span><br><span class="line">On branch main</span><br><span class="line">Your branch is up to date with <span class="string">&#x27;origin/main&#x27;</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Untracked files:</span><br><span class="line">  (use <span class="string">&quot;git add &lt;file&gt;...&quot;</span> to include <span class="keyword">in</span> what will be committed)</span><br><span class="line">        hello-world.php</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">nothing added to commit but untracked files present (use <span class="string">&quot;git add&quot;</span> to track)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="4"><li><code>git add</code> and <code>git commit</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git add hello-world.php</span><br><span class="line">$ git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;Add hello world script by php&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">[main b0dadc4] Add hello world script by php</span><br><span class="line"> 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)</span><br><span class="line"> create mode 100644 hello-world.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="5"><li><code>git log</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">log</span></span><br><span class="line">commit b0dadc41fb2bc53d5d94ee272d47d70fa58953b1 (HEAD -&gt; main)</span><br><span class="line">Author: Alowree &lt;alowree@hotmail.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Date:   Tue Aug 3 15:07:04 2021 +0800</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Add hello world script by php</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">commit 3dc8f6dfbc023e2749424481c4359e7a97651b74 (origin/main, origin/HEAD)</span><br><span class="line">Author: Alowree Xu &lt;alowree@hotmail.com&gt;</span><br><span class="line">Date:   Tue Aug 3 14:49:38 2021 +0800</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Initial commit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="6"><li><code>git push</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git push</span><br><span class="line">Enumerating objects: 4, <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Counting objects: 100% (4/4), <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Delta compression using up to 4 threads</span><br><span class="line">Compressing objects: 100% (2/2), <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Writing objects: 100% (3/3), 327 bytes | 327.00 KiB/s, <span class="keyword">done</span>.</span><br><span class="line">Total 3 (delta 0), reused 0 (delta 0), pack-reused 0</span><br><span class="line">To github.com:Alowree/Hello-World.git</span><br><span class="line">   3dc8f6d..b0dadc4  main -&gt; main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Now your code files have been published successfully on Github.</p><div class="note red icon simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-question"></i><p>What is the difference between <code>master</code> and <code>main</code> when creating repositories on Github?</p></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>开直通车应该如何出价？</title>
      <link href="/posts/373632574/"/>
      <url>/posts/373632574/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h2><p>淘宝直通车 </p><p>首页 &gt; 全部计划 &gt; 标准计划 &gt; 宝贝</p><p style="color: orange">关键词（19）</p><p>+添加关键词</p><p>在添加新的关键词时，AI会建议一个“移动出价”和一个“计算机出价”。顶部还有个“修改出价”的按钮。问题是，对于新手，我们应该直接使用AI的建议出价，还是修改出价？如果修改出价，应该向上 / 向下修改？</p><h2 id="直通车的扣费原理"><a href="#直通车的扣费原理" class="headerlink" title="直通车的扣费原理"></a>直通车的扣费原理</h2><p>为方便理解直通车的扣费原理，先放一个综合排名表的示例出来。</p><table><thead><tr><th>商家</th><th>关键词</th><th>出价（元）</th><th>原始质量分</th><th>后台显示质量分</th><th>综合排名</th><th>综合排名</th><th>单次点击实际扣费</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>A</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>2.20</td><td>2,000.00</td><td>10</td><td>4,400.00</td><td>1</td><td>1.89</td></tr><tr><td>B</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>1.98</td><td>1,900.00</td><td>10</td><td>3,762.00</td><td>2</td><td>1.02</td></tr><tr><td>C</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>1.08</td><td>1,780.00</td><td>10</td><td>1,922.40</td><td>3</td><td>0.63</td></tr><tr><td>D</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.71</td><td>1,560.00</td><td>8</td><td>1,107.60</td><td>4</td><td>0.71</td></tr><tr><td>E</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.70</td><td>1,550.00</td><td>8</td><td>1,085.00</td><td>5</td><td>0.65</td></tr><tr><td>F</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.90</td><td>1,100.00</td><td>7</td><td>990.00</td><td>6</td><td>0.90</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li><p>直通车扣费公式：关键词点击扣费 = 下一名的出价 × 下一名的质量分÷自己的关键词质量分 + 0.01元</p></li><li><p>如果综合排名已是最后一名，那么关键词点击扣费就是自己的出价。</p></li><li><p>关键词的出价≠关键词的实际扣费，但是通常，出价越高，实际扣费越高。</p></li><li><p>关键词的质量分是影响扣费的重要因素；关键词的出价影响的是关键词的综合排名。</p></li><li><p>关键词的综合排名越靠前，展现机会越多。注意，这里“展现机会”对应的是“展现次数”，而不是“点击次数”。</p></li><li><p>创意图的点击率超高，成交机会越大。</p></li><li><p>在直通车的优化中，选择哪些关键词、优化综合排名、优化点击率是车手们要攻克的难题。</p></li><li><p>关键词的综合排名 = 关键词的出价 × 关键词的质量分</p></li><li><p>质量分是系统估算的一种相对值，质量分分为计算机设备质量分和移动设备质量分。质量分是搜索推广中衡量关键词与宝贝推广信息和淘宝网用户搜索意向三者之间相关性的综合性指标。</p><ol><li><p>平常我们看到的直通车的质量分是标准化处理以后的分数，以10分制的形式来呈现</p></li><li><p>直通车计算点击扣费时使用的是直通车的原始质量分</p></li><li><p>原始质量分是没有上限的，可以趋近于无穷大</p></li></ol></li><li><p>质量分的作用主要表现在如下两个方面</p><ol><li>影响关键词的综合排名<br>综合排名=关键词的出价×关键词的质量分</li><li>影响关键词的实际扣费<br>关键词实际扣费=下一名出价×下一名的质量分÷自己的质量分+0.01元</li></ol></li><li><p>质量分和三个维度的数据有关：创意质量、相关性、买家体验。除了这3个因素以外，还有1个因素是我们在加入关键词的时候就可以看到的基础分。质量分的基础分跟帐户的权重有关。从操作上来讲，一般大词的分数会低于长尾精准关键词。</p><ul><li>创意效果实际上侧重考核图片的点击率</li></ul></li></ul><p>为了保证真正理解综合排名表，最后再贴一个示例。</p><table><thead><tr><th>商家</th><th>关键词</th><th>出价（元）</th><th>原始质量分</th><th>后台显示质量分</th><th>综合排名</th><th>综合排名</th><th>单次点击实际扣费</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>A</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.68</td><td>1,358.00</td><td>10</td><td>923.44</td><td>1</td><td>0.64</td></tr><tr><td>B</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.70</td><td>1,221.00</td><td>10</td><td>854.70</td><td>2</td><td>0.67</td></tr><tr><td>C</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>0.80</td><td>1,009.00</td><td>9</td><td>807.20</td><td>3</td><td>0.74</td></tr><tr><td>D</td><td>蓝牙音箱</td><td>1.20</td><td>613.00</td><td>7</td><td>735.60</td><td>4</td><td>1.20</td></tr></tbody></table><p>再回到我们的问题，开车应该如何出价？在“关键词”一栏，可以看到已经选定的19个关键词；在“出价”可以看到“计算机”和“移动”两个价格，鼠标靠近价格时，两个价格旁边会各出现一个铅笔图标，点击铅笔图标，会出现“出价全景图”，如下：</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/Alowree/img/raw/master/image-20210802115230971.png" alt="image-20210802115230971"></p><p>这里可以查看“建议出价”及其相应的排名区间，还可以点击“查看抢位效果”来进一步了解欲上首条、前二、前三、前六各自的需要的出价。行文至此，在本文开头提出的关于如何出价的问题其实应该更换提问方式，换成：你有多少直通车的推广预算？通过调整出价高低你想取得什么样的搜索排名位置？</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Python的文件</title>
      <link href="/posts/307/"/>
      <url>/posts/307/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>文件，就是计算机中由操作系统管理的具有名字的存储区域。内置<code>open()</code>函数会创建一个Python文件对象，可以作为计算机上的一个文件链接。与我们目前见过的类型相比，文件对象多少有点不寻常，它们不是数字、序列、也不是映射。</p><h2 id="文件操作"><a href="#文件操作" class="headerlink" title="文件操作"></a>文件操作</h2><p>在 Python 中，如果想要操作文件，首先需要创建或者打开指定的文件，并创建一个文件对象，而这些工作可以通过内置的 <code>open()</code> 函数实现。</p><h3 id="完整语法格式："><a href="#完整语法格式：" class="headerlink" title="完整语法格式："></a>完整语法格式：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">file = <span class="built_in">open</span>(file_name [, mode=<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span> [ , buffering=-<span class="number">1</span> [ , encoding = <span class="literal">None</span> ]]])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此格式中，用 <code>[]</code> 括起来的部分为可选参数，即可以使用也可以省略。其中，各个参数所代表的含义如下： </p><ul><li><code>file</code>：表示要创建的文件对象。 </li><li><code>file_name</code>：要创建或打开文件的文件名称，该名称要用引号（单引号或双引号都可以）括起来。需要注意的是，如果要打开的文件和当前执行的代码文件位于同一目录，则直接写文件名即可；否则，此参数需要指定打开文件所在的完整路径。 </li><li><code>mode</code>：可选参数，用于指定文件的打开模式。可选的打开模式如表-1 所示。如果不写，则默认以只读（<code>r</code>）模式打开文件。 </li><li><code>buffering</code>：可选参数，用于指定对文件做读写操作时，是否使用缓冲区。 </li><li><code>encoding</code>：手动设定打开文件时所使用的编码格式，不同平台的 <code>encoding</code> 参数值也不同，以 Windows 为例，其默认为 <code>cp936</code>（实际上就是 <code>GBK</code> 编码）。</li></ul><span id="more"></span><h3 id="常见用法："><a href="#常见用法：" class="headerlink" title="常见用法："></a>常见用法：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">file = <span class="built_in">open</span>(file_name,<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="推荐用法："><a href="#推荐用法：" class="headerlink" title="推荐用法："></a>推荐用法：</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(file_name,<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> file:</span><br><span class="line">    对文件进行操作</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1、打开现有的文件"><a href="#1、打开现有的文件" class="headerlink" title="1、打开现有的文件"></a>1、打开现有的文件</h3><p>如果当前目录不存在想要打开的目标文件，此时调用<code>open()</code>函数将会报错。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>file = <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">Traceback (most recent call last):</span><br><span class="line">  File <span class="string">&quot;&lt;stdin&gt;&quot;</span>, line <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">in</span> &lt;module&gt;</span><br><span class="line">FileNotFoundError: [Errno <span class="number">2</span>] No such file <span class="keyword">or</span> directory: <span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、创建当前并不存在的文件"><a href="#2、创建当前并不存在的文件" class="headerlink" title="2、创建当前并不存在的文件"></a>2、创建当前并不存在的文件</h3><p>可以通过传递<code>mode</code>参数，以写入模式打开文件的方式，来生成一个全新的文件，并在文件对象中写入内容。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>file = <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>file.write(<span class="string">&#x27;This is a new file!&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">19</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>file.close()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>file.closed</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> os</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>os.getcwd()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;C:\\Users\\Administrator&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、写入和读取文件"><a href="#3、写入和读取文件" class="headerlink" title="3、写入和读取文件"></a>3、写入和读取文件</h3><p>在任何情况下，Python程序中的文件都采用字符串的形式进行读写。读取文件时会返回字符串<code>str</code>形式的文本，写文件的时候是将文本以字符串<code>str</code>形式传递给<code>write()</code>方法。文件对象常用的写入和读取方法有下面5个：</p><ul><li>  <code>file.write(str)</code></li><li>  <code>file.writelines(list)</code></li><li>  <code>file.read([size])</code></li><li>  <code>file.readline()</code></li><li>  <code>file.readlines()</code></li></ul><p>我们现在有一个目标文件了，存储在当前目录<code>C:\Users\Administrator</code>下面。对于新手来说，除非你对当前路径、相对路径和绝对路径等相关知识非常熟悉，否则建议使用清晰明确的绝对路径<code>C:\Users\Administrator\a.txt</code>来指定需要操作的文件。下面，我们先往文件里面多添加一些内容，然后再来进行打开和读取操作。我们使用<code>with</code>语句管理上下文。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    f.write(<span class="string">&#x27;I write some more data.\n2nd line. \n3rd line. \nI love Python.&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">60</span>              <span class="comment"># 返回写入的字符数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="built_in">len</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;I write some more data.\n2nd line. \n3rd line. \nI love Python.&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">60</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    data_1 = <span class="built_in">list</span>(f)</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    data_2 = f.readlines()</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="built_in">print</span>(data_1)</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&#x27;This is a new file!I write some more data.\n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2nd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;3rd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;I love Python.&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="built_in">print</span>(data_2)</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&#x27;This is a new file!I write some more data.\n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2nd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;3rd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;I love Python.&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>data_1 == data_2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.read())                     <span class="comment"># 读取全部文件内容</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">This <span class="keyword">is</span> a new file!I write some more data.</span><br><span class="line">2nd line. </span><br><span class="line">3rd line. </span><br><span class="line">I love Python.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readline())                 <span class="comment"># 读取文件的第一行</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">This <span class="keyword">is</span> a new file!I write some more data.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readlines())                <span class="comment"># 按行读取文件，返回行内容的列表</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&#x27;This is a new file!I write some more data.\n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2nd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;3rd line. \n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;I love Python.&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;w&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:           <span class="comment"># 覆盖原来文件内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    f.write(<span class="string">&#x27;0123456789&#x27;</span>)               <span class="comment"># 返回写入的字符数</span></span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.read())</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">0123456789</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    f.writelines(<span class="built_in">list</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;ABCDEF&#x27;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.read())</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">0123456789ABCDEF            <span class="comment"># writelines()先把列表拼接成字符串，再写入，没有换行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    f.writelines([<span class="string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;I\n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Love\n&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Shenzhen\n&#x27;</span>])</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.read())</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">0123456789ABCDEF            <span class="comment"># 如果换行，需要手动加入\n</span></span><br><span class="line">I</span><br><span class="line">Love</span><br><span class="line">Shenzhen</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>f                       <span class="comment"># f变量仍然可用</span></span><br><span class="line">&lt;_io.TextIOWrapper name=<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span> mode=<span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span> encoding=<span class="string">&#x27;cp936&#x27;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>f.closed, f.encoding    <span class="comment"># 可以读取f对象的属性</span></span><br><span class="line">(<span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;cp936&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>f.read()                <span class="comment"># 但是不能在f上执行I/O操作，因为在with块的末尾，调用TextIOWrapper.__exit__方法把文件关闭了。</span></span><br><span class="line">Traceback (most recent call last):</span><br><span class="line">  File <span class="string">&quot;&lt;stdin&gt;&quot;</span>, line <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">in</span> &lt;module&gt;</span><br><span class="line">ValueError: I/O operation on closed file.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;a.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readline())         <span class="comment"># 体会readline()和文件指针的关系</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readline())</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readline())</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">... </span>    <span class="built_in">print</span>(f.readline())</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">0123456789ABCDEF</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">I</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Love</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Shenzhen</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、文件打开模式"><a href="#4、文件打开模式" class="headerlink" title="4、文件打开模式"></a>4、文件打开模式</h3><p><strong>表-1 <code>open() </code>函数支持的文件打开模式</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th>模式</th><th>意义</th><th>注意事项</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>r</td><td>只读模式打开文件，读文件内容的指针会放在文件的开头。</td><td>文件必须存在。如果当前目录不存在想要打开的文件，解释器会报错。</td></tr><tr><td>r+</td><td>打开文件后，既可以从头读取文件内容，也可以从开头向文件中写入新的内容，写入的新内容会覆盖文件中等长度的原有内容。</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>rb</td><td>以二进制格式、采用只读模式打开文件，读文件内容的指针位于文件的开头，一般用于非文本文件，如图片文件、音频文件等。</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>rb+</td><td>以二进制格式、采用读写模式打开文件，读写文件的指针会放在文件的开头，通常针对非文本文件（如音频文件）。</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>w</td><td>以只写模式打开文件，若该文件存在，打开时会清空文件中原有的内容。</td><td>若文件存在，会清空其原有内容（覆盖文件）；反之，则创建新文件。</td></tr><tr><td>w+</td><td>打开文件后，会对原有内容进行清空，并对该文件有读写权限。<br><font color="red">都清空了，还怎么读取？！</font></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>wb</td><td>正整数以二进制格式、只写模式打开文件，一般用于非文本文件（如音频文件）</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>wb+</td><td>以二进制格式、读写模式打开文件，一般用于非文本文件</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>a</td><td>以追加模式打开一个文件，对文件只有写入权限，如果文件已经存在，文件指针将放在文件的末尾（即新写入内容会位于已有内容之后）；反之，则会创建新文件。</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>a+</td><td>以读写模式打开文件；如果文件存在，文件指针放在文件的末尾（新写入文件会位于已有内容之后）；反之，则创建新文件。<br><font color="red">在这个状态下，文件指针在文件的末尾，还怎么读取文件？</font></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ab</td><td>以二进制格式打开文件，并采用追加模式，对文件只有写权限。如果该文件已存在，文件指针位于文件末尾（新写入文件会位于已有内容之后）；反之，则创建新文件。</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ab+</td><td>以二进制模式打开文件，并采用追加模式，对文件具有读写权限，如果文件存在，则文件指针位于文件的末尾（新写入文件会位于已有内容之后）；反之，则创建新文件。<br><font color="red">在这个状态下，文件指针在文件的末尾，还怎么读取文件？</font></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>鉴于实施爬虫进行数据分析的时候，我们一般只需要处理文本文件，所以暂时先不研究以二进制格式（<code>b</code>和<code>b+</code>）打开文件。这样的话，处理文本文件我们暂时只需要研究下面六种读写模式，尤其需要验证表-1中红色字体提问的三种带<code>+</code>的模式。</p><p><strong>表-2 文件打开模式之逻辑比较</strong></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">    start(打开文件) --&gt; conditionA&#123;用于&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    conditionA -- 读 --&gt; printR[r]</span><br><span class="line">    conditionA -- 写 --&gt; conditionB&#123;是否清空&#125;</span><br><span class="line">conditionA -- 读/写 --&gt; conditionC&#123;是否清空&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    conditionB -- YES --&gt; printW[w]</span><br><span class="line">    conditionB -- NO --&gt; printA[a]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">conditionC --YES --&gt; printWW[w+]</span><br><span class="line">conditionC --NO --&gt; conditionD&#123;指针位置&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">conditionD --开头--&gt; printRR[r+]</span><br><span class="line">conditionD --结尾--&gt; printAA[a+]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><p>[1]<a href="http://c.biancheng.net/view/2544.html">Python open()函数详解：打开指定文件</a> </p><p>[2]<a href="http://c.biancheng.net/view/7540.html">HTML<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签（表格）</a> </p><p>[3]<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_32042527/article/details/88084130">Markdown表格合并单元格</a> </p><p>[4]<a href="http://soft.xiaoshujiang.com/docs/grammar/feature/mermaid/">小书匠语法说明之mermaid</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
